      </mj-section>

      <mj-section mj-class="pb-16">
        <mj-column>
          <mj-divider />

          <mj-text mj-class="heading-3 c-blue pb-8">
            Stuck inside these four walls
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text mj-class="pb-8">
            Sent inside forever. Never seeing no one. Nice again like you. Mama you, mama...
          </mj-text>
