        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>

      <mj-section>
        <mj-column>
          <mj-divider />

          <mj-text mj-class="heading-3 c-blue pb-8">
            What I feel, I can't say
          </mj-text>
          <mj-text mj-class="pb-8">
            But my love is there for you, any time of day. But if it's not love that you need...
          </mj-text>
